p: \rIt's not a very nice place, but we couldn't think of a better one to talk.
\rI heard you talking about Mew as I was walking by the Gym...
\rYou should tell your friend to be careful with what he says!\nNow that we know you have Mew, we'll have to take it away from you!
\rSo here's the deal.\nRight now, your friend is trapped!\nIf you give us Mew, we'll let him out.
\rSo, what do you say?\nLet's make this easy for all of us!
\rIf you won't give it to us voluntarily...
\rWe'll take you out now, and take the Mew by force!
\rSince you don't seem to be listening, kid, I'll take matters into my own hands.\nWe can't convince you, so I'll ask Mew itself!
\rMew, I know you can hear me!
\rRight now, that boy is trapped on an island in a pond of green gunk.
\rWe know you're going to help him eventually, and we're willing to wait.
\rIt'll make this easier if you just appeared to us now!
\bMew... you came?\nBut... you can't leave \pn alone!
\rBwa ha ha ha!\nPokemon like Mew are far too predictable.
\rNow, Mew. It's time to join a new side!\nWelc-
\bShaymin purified the water using its Seed Flare
\rWhat... Shaymin...?\nWhy is Shaymin, another of the pixie legendaries here?
\rDid Mew call upon it for help?\nWe can't take on two legendaries at once!\nAbyssal Cult, retreat for now!
\rYou better watch it, \pn! We'll be back for that Mew soon enough!
\bYou want to travel with me?\nThat's... incredible. I can't believe a legendary Pokemon would choose me.
\bBut that means... the prophecy could be about either me or \pn.
\bI need to go find Nora and tell her all the good news.\nI'll meet up with you later, \pn.\nAnd thanks for rescuing me, I appreciate it.
Obtained the \rShaymin DNA\c[0].\nMew can now use Shaymin's DNA to transform and use the Seed Flare ability outside of battle.
\rIn all honesty, I wasn't expecting you to.
\rWe heard you talking about Mew as I was walking by the Gym...
\rYou know, someone who has a chance of being the hero of a prophecy and saving the world should be a little bit more careful about what they might say.
\rSo here's the deal.\nYou give us Mew in exchange for your friend.
\rIf you won't give it to us voluntarily...
\rWe'll take you out now, and take the Mew by force!
\rSince you don't seem to be listening, kid, I'll take matters into my own hands.\nWe can't convince you, so I'll ask Mew itself!
\rThis green liquid on the ground is heavily polluted!
\rIt is also highly corrosive!\nFalling into it would kill a person in seconds!
\rNow, if you don't appear to me, I will push this child- Damian- into the pool!
\rYou wouldn't want that, would you?\nThe end of an innocent life?
\bMew... you came?\nBut... you can't leave \pn alone!
\rHahaha!\nPokemon like Mew are far too predictable.
\rNow,  Mew.\nIf you want these children to stay alive, come here.\nIt's time for you to leave \pn and join us instead.
\bShaymin purified the water using its Seed Flare
\rWhat? Shaymin...?\nWhy is Shaymin, another of the pixie legendaries here?
\rDid Mew call upon it for help?\nWe can't take on two legendaries at once!\nAbyssal Cult, retreat for now!
\r\pn... Damian...\nYou better believe we'll be back soon.

You want to travel with me?
But that's incredible!
Does that mean that I'm...
I'm one of the companions of a pixie Pokemon?
Wow, I didn't think I was that

\bAnd now the Abyssal Cult knows that Mew and Shaymin have chosen us...
\bWe need to be very careful.\nI can't use Shaymin except when it's safe.
\bI need to go find Nora and tell her all the good news.\nI'll meet up with you later, \pn.\nAnd thanks for rescuing me, I appreciate it.

\rYou won't get away from us this time!
pbTrainerBattle(PBTrainers::ABYSSALGRUNT_FKING,"Cultist",_I("We only want one thing. After that's done, you and your friend will be free to leave."),false,0)
\rWe have your friend. Don't even think about running away.
pbTrainerBattle(PBTrainers::ABYSSALGRUNT_FKING,"Cultist",_I("We only want one thing. After that's done, you and your friend will be free to leave."),false,0)
\rWe only want one thing. After that's done, you and your friend will be free to leave.
\bYou think you can beat me?\nSorry, kid, but that's naive.\nI'm the strongest trainer there is!
An item appeared from the past!
\rMuah ha ha ha!\nSoon, the Abyssal Cult will be unstoppable!
\bI don't care what any prophecy says. No kid is taking me down!
\bYou really think you can take me on? I'm one of the strongest grunts here!
\rWe're the Abyssal Cult.\nWe worship only Water-type Pokemon.\nAnd very soon, the strongest of them all will belong to us!
pbTrainerBattle(PBTrainers::ABYSSALGRUNT_FCRAW,"Cultist",_I("Don't interefere with our plans, or you'll pay!"),false,0)
\rDon't interefere with our plans, or you'll pay!
\rI don't waste time with words.\nBring it.
pbTrainerBattle(PBTrainers::ABYSSALGRUNT_FKING,"Cultist",_I("Obey us, and you might leave unscathed."),false,0)
\rYour friend awaits you. If you don't do everything we say, well, let's just say he won't be alive to complain about it, hmm?
